## 2. 📂 Best Repository Structure

```
github.com/bksanket99/
│
├── 📌 bksanket99/              ← Profile README (pinned, this file)
│
├── 📦 wordpress-snippets/      ← Custom PHP snippets, hooks, filters
│   └── README.md, /snippets/*.php
│
├── 🛒 woocommerce-customizations/ ← WooCommerce mods, gateway configs
│   └── README.md, /plugins/*.php
│
├── ⚡ wp-performance-toolkit/  ← PageSpeed, caching, Cloudflare configs
│   └── README.md, guides, .htaccess examples
│
├── 🔌 acf-field-groups/        ← Exported ACF JSON field groups
│   └── README.md, /json/*.json
│
├── 🎨 elementor-templates/     ← Custom Elementor widgets/templates
│   └── README.md, /templates/*.json
│
├── 🔒 wp-security-checklist/   ← Security hardening guide + config
│   └── README.md, checklist.md
│
├── 📋 wp-project-boilerplate/  ← Starter theme / project scaffold
│   └── README.md, /src/
│
└── 📄 resume/                  ← PDF resume for recruiters
    └── Sanket_Baviskar_WordPress_Developer.pdf
```

**Rules:**
- Every repo needs a clear `README.md` with description, tech stack, and screenshots
- Add `Topics` tags: `wordpress`, `woocommerce`, `php`, `elementor`, `acf`
- Pin your 6 best repos on your profile

