## 8. 📈 Profile Improvement Roadmap

### Month 1 — Foundation
- [ ] Push README.md to `bksanket99/bksanket99` repo
- [ ] Set up GitHub profile (bio, location, website, pinned repos)
- [ ] Create `wordpress-snippets` repo with 10 useful PHP snippets
- [ ] Create `woocommerce-customizations` repo
- [ ] Upload resume PDF to a `resume` repo

### Month 2 — Activity & Visibility
- [ ] Publish `wp-performance-toolkit` repo (PageSpeed guide + configs)
- [ ] Create `acf-field-groups` repo with exported JSON
- [ ] Contribute 1 PR to WooCommerce or Elementor
- [ ] Start posting on LinkedIn (2x/week)
- [ ] Add GitHub link to Naukri, LinkedIn, Internshala

### Month 3 — Authority Building
- [ ] Publish a WordPress plugin on wordpress.org
- [ ] Write a dev.to or Hashnode article: "My WooCommerce Razorpay Integration Story"
- [ ] Get 50+ GitHub followers via community engagement
- [ ] Reach out directly to 10 WordPress agencies in Pune/Mumbai on LinkedIn

### Month 4–6 — Scale
- [ ] 100+ GitHub stars across repos
- [ ] 500+ LinkedIn connections (targeted: HR, CTOs, WP agencies)
- [ ] Get first freelance client from GitHub/LinkedIn discovery
- [ ] Apply to remote WordPress roles (Automattic, Yoast, WP Engine ecosystem)

